      <scopecontent id="aspace_5310b9e63a84d1d201ea48c00650fd82">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reports and administrative files of the Yale Department of Physics documenting the Wright Nuclear Structure Laboratory and the construction of the Sloane Physics Laboratory. Also included is a library circulation book.</p>  
